<li sourcefile="supply-chain/pim/tasks/create-sales-price-selection-criteria.md" sourcestartlinenumber="52">Click Edit.</li>
<li sourcefile="supply-chain/pim/tasks/create-sales-price-selection-criteria.md" sourcestartlinenumber="53">In the Table field, select Customers.</li>
<li sourcefile="supply-chain/pim/tasks/create-sales-price-selection-criteria.md" sourcestartlinenumber="54">In the Field field, select Customer group.
<ul sourcefile="supply-chain/pim/tasks/create-sales-price-selection-criteria.md" sourcestartlinenumber="55">
<li sourcefile="supply-chain/pim/tasks/create-sales-price-selection-criteria.md" sourcestartlinenumber="55">In this example, we will use a specific customer group for the selection criteria.</li>
</ul>
</li>
